data.description: Serene and private 3-bedroom 2 bath lake home is move in ready! Large corner lot & Beautiful Lake views from the HUGE double deck. Walking distance to Spring Lake & large neighborhood gazebo! Spacious kitchen w/ new countertops, backsplash, SS appliances & a farmhouse sink. Lots of living space including a separate laundry room, HUGE Den, & Dining Room with built in China cabinet. Large storage building/workshop, 2 decks for entertaining. Fresh paint throughout. No city taxes! Show and sell!!!
